# Software Architecture Coursework – Sprint 2 Report

## 1. Introduction

This sprint focuses on deriving a software architecture from the requirements defined in Sprint 1. The system developed is a **Share Data Retrieval System**, which allows users to request historical share price data within a specified date range.

The architecture follows **Clean Architecture principles**, ensuring separation of concerns, maintainability, and scalability.

